  schema:teaches &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/cybernetic-postliberalism/terms/californication/> , &lt;https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/sociology/domains/cybernetic-postliberalism/terms/genre-calibration/> , "Feeling Rules under Californication" ;
